description: The SPDR S&P China ETF seeks to provide investment results that, before fees and expenses, correspond generally to the total return performance of the S&P China BMI IndexSeeks to provide exposure to the investable universe of publicly traded companies domiciled in China that are available to foreign investorsMay also include China A Shares available via the Shanghai-Hong Kong Stock Connect or Shenzhen-Hong Kong Stock Connect Facilities
name: SPDR S&P China ETF
